This is only preliminary early developement version.
It *may work* or *may destroy your system*.
Use it on your own risk!

Installation:
=============

Requirements:
-------------
 libfribidi-dev

Install:
--------

 As user run:
 $ make
 Then as superuser
 # make install
 
 If you want to use a path different from
 the default /usr/local/bin/ you need to
 edit the makefile (change INSTPATH)

Uninstall:
----------

 As superuser
 # make uninstall
